genresAdvancedInfo.name: luxembourgian indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Luxembourgian indie music is a diverse and eclectic genre that encompasses a wide range of styles and influences. It is characterized by its emphasis on creativity, experimentation, and individuality, and is often associated with underground and alternative music scenes. From dreamy shoegaze to upbeat pop, Luxembourgian indie music is a vibrant and exciting part of the country's musical landscape.
